The MIT license above covers the code in this repository (the R scripts).

The data files under data/ are redistributed from public sources — the City of
Chicago Data Portal (crimes ijzp-q8t2, shooting victims vqmv-zqjm, community-area
boundaries), the Chicago Police Department CLEARMAP gang-territory maps, and the
U.S. Census Bureau American Community Survey. They remain subject to the terms of
their respective providers. Please cite both this package and the original data
sources when reusing them.
